# ─── Audio masters — NEVER delete this again ──────────────────────────────
# content/audio/masters/ holds RJM track WAV files, hard-linked from
# ~/Downloads/Music/Tracks/ (+ loose Selah.wav in ~/Downloads/). Files are
# large (60+ MB each) and git-ignored. Directory structure kept only by
# presence of .gitkeep. NEVER allow git to overwrite this path with a
# symlink or anything else — the Apr 22 2026 merge did exactly that and
# nearly lost the Selah master.
content/audio/
!content/audio/.gitkeep
.worktrees/
.claude_subprocess_home/
